# CODEC — Coder's Development & Evolution Command Center
## Master Product Requirements Document (Unified PRD)

> **One App. Typing Mastery + Learning OS. Built to make you independent.**

---

## 1. App Identity

| Field | Value |
|-------|-------|
| **Name** | CODEC — Coder's Development & Evolution Command Center |
| **Tagline** | Type better. Learn deeper. Build smarter. |
| **Users** | Multi-user with authentication (registration + login) |
| **Context** | Generic learning platform — not tied to any single project |
| **Storage** | MongoDB (cloud/local) — full backend with user accounts |
| **AI** | Single Gemini model (API key in `.env` server-side) |

---

## 2. System Architecture

### 2.1 Technology Stack

| Layer | Technology | Why |
|-------|-----------|-----|
| **Frontend** | Vite + React 18 (JSX) | Fast HMR, clean component model |
| **Styling** | Tailwind CSS v3 | Utility-first, rapid dark theme implementation, excellent for neon effects |
| **State (client)** | Zustand | Lightweight, simple API, syncs with backend |
| **Routing** | React Router v6 | Clean URL-based page navigation |
| **Backend** | Node.js + Express.js | REST API layer between React and MongoDB |
| **Database** | MongoDB + Mongoose | Document-based storage, flexible schemas, user accounts |
| **Auth** | JWT (JSON Web Tokens) | Stateless auth with bcrypt password hashing |
| **Code Editor** | Monaco Editor (React) | VS Code engine in browser |
| **Python Runtime** | Pyodide (CDN) | Real Python in browser via WebAssembly |
| **Charts** | Recharts | React-native, composable, great with dark themes |
| **Icons** | Lucide React | Clean, consistent, tree-shakeable |
| **AI** | Google Gemini API (single model) | API key stored server-side in `.env` |
| **ML Pipeline** | Python + scikit-learn | 3-model typing analysis, trained on user data via API |
| **Animations** | [React Bits](https://reactbits.dev/) | 110+ animated components for stunning UI |
| **Notifications** | Browser Notification API | Study reminders, no library needed |

