## 3. Authentication & Multi-User System

### 3.1 Auth Flow

| Screen | Route | Purpose |
|--------|-------|---------|
| **Register** | `/register` | Name, email, password, confirm password |
| **Login** | `/login` | Email + password → JWT token |
| **Protected Routes** | `/*` | All app routes require valid JWT |

### 3.2 User Model (MongoDB)

```javascript
{
  _id: ObjectId,
  name: String,
  email: String (unique),
  password: String (bcrypt hashed),
  avatar: String (default generated),
  createdAt: Date,
  
  // Profile
  activeTechId: String,
  onboardingComplete: Boolean,
  weeklyHourTarget: Number (default: 3),
  reminderEnabled: Boolean,
  reminderTime: String,
  
  // Gamification
  xp: Number (default: 0),
  level: Number (default: 1),
  rank: String (default: "Dormant NPC"),
  streak: { count: Number, lastDate: Date, type: String },
  
  // Gate
  lastGateDate: String,
  gateSkipCount: Number,
  gateDurationMinutes: Number (default: 5),
}
```

