## 5. The 12 Pages — Full Specifications

### ⚙️ 1. Settings `/settings`

| Feature | Detail |
|---------|--------|
| **Profile** | Edit name, avatar |
| **Active Technology** | Dropdown of 10 techs — sets current tech for Dashboard & Tutor context |
| **Gate Duration** | Selector: 1 / 2 / 3 / 5 / 10 minutes |
| **Weekly Hour Target** | Number input, default 3 |
| **Study Reminder** | Toggle + time picker (Browser Notifications API) |
| **Account** | Change password, logout, delete account (requires typing DELETE) |
| **About** | App version, stack summary |

---

### 🏠 2. Dashboard `/`

Your daily status board — opens every session after the gate.

| Component | Detail |
|-----------|--------|
| **XP + Level Bar** | Top of page. Current XP, XP to next level, NPC rank. Dual-colour segments: typing XP (neon green) vs learning XP (neon purple). |
| **Streak Badge** | Flame counter with animated tiers (see §7.3). |
| **Status Board** | Mixed checklist of today's tasks from both systems: gate, current week's learning task, flashcard review, mini project check-in. Checkboxes award XP. |
| **Study Timer** | Auto-running timer in TopBar. Pauses on tab blur. |
| **Quick Stats Row** | 4 neon cards — Total Hours This Week, Current WPM, Tech Progress %, Sessions Today. |
| **Study Chart** | Recharts area chart — daily hours over last 14 days. Two series: typing time (green) + learning time (purple). |
| **Next Action Card** | Gemini-generated (or static fallback): "Your most impactful action right now is..." |
| **Recent Achievements** | Last 3 badges earned as neon cards. |

---

### ⌨️ 3. Typing `/typing`

Your typing dojo — practice, lessons, stats, ML analysis, and finger guide.

**Five Tabs:**

#### Tab 1: Practice
- Free typing session. Mode selector: **Words / Code / Sentences**
- Duration selector: **1 / 3 / 5 / 10 min**
- Live typing engine with character-by-character highlighting
- WPM + accuracy update every 5 seconds
- SVG keyboard below shows correct finger for next key
- Session data sent to MongoDB on completion via API

#### Tab 2: Lessons
- **8-level structured curriculum** starting from absolute basics:

| Level | Name | Keys | WPM Target |
|-------|------|------|-----------|
| L1 | Home Row Basics | `a s d f` — `j k l ;` | 15 WPM |
| L2 | Home Row Mastery | All home row + spacebar rhythm | 20 WPM |
| L3 | Upper Row | `q w e r t` — `y u i o p` | 25 WPM |
| L4 | Lower Row | `z x c v b` — `n m , . /` | 30 WPM |
| L5 | Full Alphabet | All 26 letters combined | 35 WPM |
| L6 | Numbers Row | `1 2 3 4 5` — `6 7 8 9 0` | 38 WPM |
| L7 | Symbols & Punctuation | `! @ # $ % ^ & * ( ) _ + - = [ ] { }` etc. | 40 WPM |
| L8 | Code Mode | Real Python, C++, JS snippets | 50 WPM |

- Each level: 4–6 lessons + level test (85%+ accuracy to pass and unlock next)
- **AI Bonus Drills** section — up to 3 Gemini-assigned drills based on ML analysis (optional, 30 XP each)

#### Tab 3: Stats
- WPM chart (line, last 30 sessions)
- Accuracy chart
- Keyboard heatmap (SVG keys coloured by performance)
- Finger performance bar chart (8 fingers)
- Top 20 slowest bigrams list
- Session history table (last 20)
- Personal bests per mode

#### Tab 4: ML Analysis
- **"Run Analysis"** button → calls Express endpoint → runs Python ML → displays results
- Displays: profile summary, 3 ranked improvement actions, WPM projection chart, typing fingerprint card
- **"Get AI Overview"** button (optional, user-triggered) → sends ML report to Gemini → shows AI coaching advice + 3 bonus drills
- Last-updated timestamp with orange badge if >7 days old

#### Tab 5: Finger Guide
- Full static SVG QWERTY keyboard, colour-coded by finger assignment
- Hover tooltip on each key
- Finger legend below keyboard

