## 8. Design System — Surprise Theme

### 8.1 Theme: "Cyberpunk Command Center"

A dark, immersive cyberpunk aesthetic — not generic dark mode, but a **full terminal-meets-gaming** experience.

| Token | Value | Usage |
|-------|-------|-------|
| `--bg-primary` | `#0A0E1A` | Main background — deep space blue-black |
| `--bg-card` | `#111827` | Card/panel backgrounds |
| `--bg-elevated` | `#1A2035` | Elevated surfaces, modals |
| `--text-primary` | `#E2E8F0` | Main text |
| `--text-muted` | `#64748B` | Secondary text |
| `--neon-cyan` | `#00F5D4` | Primary accent, success states |
| `--neon-magenta` | `#F72585` | Secondary accent, warnings |
| `--neon-blue` | `#4361EE` | Informational, links |
| `--neon-gold` | `#FFD60A` | XP, achievements, highlights |
| `--neon-orange` | `#FF6B35` | Streak, urgency |
| `--neon-purple` | `#7B2FF7` | AI responses, learning system |
| `--border-dim` | `#1E293B` | Card borders (default) |

### 8.2 React Bits Animations — Where to Use

| Component | React Bits Component | Where Used |
|-----------|---------------------|-----------|
| **Splash Screen** | `Aurora` background + `ShuffleText` | App load, 1.5 seconds |
| **Page Transitions** | `FadeContent` | Between page navigations |
| **Typing Text** | `SplitText` (letter-by-letter reveal) | Gate screen intro text |
| **Achievement Unlock** | `Confetti` + `Spotlight` | Badge unlock celebration |
| **XP Gain** | `CountUp` (animated number) | XP changes on Dashboard |
| **Streak Fire** | `Sparkles` particles | Gold/Diamond streak flames |
| **Card Hovers** | `TiltCard` | NeonCard hover effect |
| **Loading States** | `RotatingText` | While ML model runs |
| **Dashboard Stats** | `CountUp` | Stat card number animations |
| **Sidebar Active** | `GlowEffect` | Active nav item indicator |
| **Gate Timer** | `GradientText` | Countdown timer digits |
| **Error States** | `GlitchText` | Error messages, streak broken |
| **Background** | `Particles` (subtle, low opacity) | Behind main content area |

### 8.3 Typography

| Usage | Font | Source |
|-------|------|--------|
| **Headings** | `Bricolage Grotesque` | Google Fonts |
| **Body** | `Inter` | Google Fonts |
| **Code/Mono** | `JetBrains Mono` | Google Fonts |
| **Accent/Rank** | `Orbitron` | Google Fonts (for NPC rank titles) |

### 8.4 Key Design Rules

1. **Never white backgrounds** — everything is `--bg-primary` or darker
2. **Neon = accent only** — text and borders glow, backgrounds stay dark
3. **Cards have subtle glow on hover** — `border-color` transitions to neon, faint `box-shadow`
4. **All interactive elements pulse** — buttons, active states, timers
5. **Micro-animations everywhere** — number counters animate, progress bars fill smoothly, cards tilt on hover

