## 9. MongoDB Schema — Complete

### Collections

| Collection | Key Fields |
|-----------|------------|
| `users` | name, email, password (hashed), profile settings, XP/level/streak, gateDuration |
| `typingSessions` | userId, date, mode, duration, wpm, accuracy, keypresses[], backspaces[] |
| `progress` | userId, techProgress {}, weekCompletions [], projectProgress {} |
| `notes` | userId, techId, content (markdown), lastEdited, wordCount |
| `achievements` | userId, unlockedBadges [], unlockedDates {} |
| `chatHistory` | userId, messages [] (last 50), createdAt |
| `codeSnippets` | userId, name, language, code, createdAt |
| `mlAnalysis` | userId, report (JSON), geminiAdvice (JSON), createdAt |
| `flashcardProgress` | userId, cardId, timesReviewed, timesCorrect, difficulty |
| `scheduleWeeks` | userId, weekNumber, techId, topic, task, targetHours, completed |

