## 12. API Endpoints Summary

| Method | Route | Purpose |
|--------|-------|---------|
| POST | `/api/auth/register` | Create account |
| POST | `/api/auth/login` | Login → JWT |
| GET | `/api/auth/me` | Get current user |
| PUT | `/api/auth/profile` | Update profile/settings |
| POST | `/api/typing/session` | Save typing session data |
| GET | `/api/typing/sessions` | Get user's session history |
| GET | `/api/typing/stats` | Get typing stats summary |
| POST | `/api/ml/analyze` | Trigger ML analysis |
| GET | `/api/ml/report` | Get latest ML report |
| POST | `/api/ml/gemini-overview` | Get Gemini AI overview of ML report |
| GET | `/api/progress` | Get user progress (XP, level, etc.) |
| PUT | `/api/progress` | Update progress |
| GET | `/api/flashcards` | Get flashcards (filtered by tech) |
| PUT | `/api/flashcards/:id/progress` | Update card review status |
| GET/POST/PUT/DELETE | `/api/schedule` | CRUD for schedule weeks |
| GET/PUT | `/api/notes/:techId` | Get/update notes for a tech |
| GET/POST/DELETE | `/api/snippets` | Saved code snippets |
| GET/POST | `/api/tutor/chat` | AI Tutor conversation |
| GET | `/api/achievements` | Get user's badges |
| POST | `/api/achievements/check` | Check & unlock new badges |

